{"tid":387642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意睇藝術/歷史展，係咪好異類？","createTime":"2017-09-04T19:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T14:20:50.000Z","uid":117627,"like":19,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc77288c355765f0518045ec09b65503a61d23c","tid":387642,"uid":117627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:33:03.000Z","msg":"歷史博物館今日行咗<br />\n隔離嘅木乃伊睇埋<br />\n聽日星期二文化博物館唔開<br />\n藝術館裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打有其他介紹"},{"pid":"7abac2f3a3f9430e9eb628e53a3298f77e0f62a1","tid":387642,"uid":126902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歷史博物館今日行咗<br />\n隔離嘅木乃伊睇埋<br />\n聽日星期二文化博物館唔開<br />\n藝術館裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打有其他介紹</blockquote><br />\n歷史文化科學呢三個館入場人數唔少<br />\n次次有啲勁嘢睇都好多人(如木乃伊 如漢朝文物)<br />\n反而香港藝術館讀中學果陣去過完全無人"},{"pid":"1f59d5b69ce1b945a8ed7e91f8c06fb0c4cf877e","tid":387642,"uid":17268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:44:32.000Z","msg":"好多年輕人都有樓主你呢個想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e73eeaf58c9b86b36eb392a9624a35636ec49a","tid":387642,"uid":117627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:51:17.000Z","msg":"主要想問下依排有無咩畫展啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n襯有時間想睇多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83981e1c4de3f29c6f613430b1d0b9c65d99fb57","tid":387642,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:59:06.000Z","msg":"去一轉巴黎，睇到你出曬水都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971a65fb900afa2df2e77b6fc6224ef9709a932f","tid":387642,"uid":46737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"repl