,{"pid":"0dcbe42e5f17f5ee927aec4497182e29801fc215","tid":387642,"uid":34184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"舊藝術館 太多中國野<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係對中國特別興趣會覺得悶"},{"pid":"625b0e754db958c707e809f2963ee2ac422e5833","tid":387642,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊藝術館 太多中國野<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係對中國特別興趣會覺得悶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n特展會有多d野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504fbc045606c3d8089a48cc6eda3571932ad671","tid":387642,"uid":115998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔係異類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細細個既夢想就係想做考古學家<br />\n<br />\n利申：而家係濕鳩打工仔一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c7b83786d5e1215a33788aeaaeb12bf73c75d2","tid":387642,"uid":34427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"唔會呀<br />\n之前去新加坡同沖繩<br />\n都去左藝術館睇左三個幾鐘<br />\n明明唔係讀art 講唔上有冇咩評賞<br />\n但睇完個下好滿足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d6cee10fec828704a0a2f1f4145906305ccef5","tid":387642,"uid":36968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"樓主係會睇睇前/睇完做research<br />\n定求其睇完就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86767bba342ee290eb9f886bf8033b68e118a33","tid":387642,"uid":106027,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"咁都覺得自己小眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb8f37cd5f679725a0c76bfa920c8626de8ef13","tid":387642,"uid":133123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:24:47.000Z","m